            <span>On-site: 8 hrs</span>
            <span>Outcome: Full recovery</span>
          </div>
          <p>An H2XX module was unable to operate normally after extended high-load running without scheduled maintenance. Remote diagnosis identified a likely baseboard fault. Four senior engineers arrived on-site within 8 hours.</p>
